00:30:09.620 --> 00:30:12.460
of what the exoplanet
atmospheres could really be like.

00:30:12.460 --> 00:30:16.080
So it's just a very exciting time
to be in any area of astrophysics

00:30:16.080 --> 00:30:18.200
because anything that
you do has some tie

00:30:18.200 --> 00:30:21.830
in to understanding the
atmosphere's around these planets.

00:30:21.830 --> 00:30:25.770 position:56%
So we know the planets are there and
